    <stitle>5 SPEED AND 6 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - REMOVE - CLUTCH HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>CLUTCH HOUSING</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Removal of the clutch housing is done in the horizontal position.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>The clutch release mechanism must be removed.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bolts from outside the clutch housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302609">Figure 9</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302609" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302609" filename="../figg13/g1302609.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 9. Remove Bolts From Outside Clutch Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Jar the clutch housing to break the gasket seal (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302609">Figure 9</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Pull the clutch housing from the transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302610">Figure 10</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302610" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302610" filename="../figg13/g1302610.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 10. Pull Clutch Housing From Transmission Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
